    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable and comfortable choice for a daily driver. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, while the exterior shows only minor signs of use consistent with its age. All electronics and features are fully functional, and the car has a clear service history. It\u2019s a dependable car ready for its next owner.",
