    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, representing a rare find for any serious collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single blemish or scratch. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with every surface appearing as if it just left the factory floor, and all features functioning perfectly. This car has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring it remains in peak condition.",
